Action: string; What type of record is this. login | logout.
Allowed: bool; If request was allowed or denied.
AppDomain: string; The domain of the Application that Access is protecting.
Connection: string; Identity provider used for the login.
CreatedAt: int or string; The date and time the corresponding access request was made (for example, '2021-07-27T00:01:07Z').
Email: string; Email of the user who logged in.
IPAddress: string; The IP address of the client.
PurposeJustificationPrompt: string; Message prompted to the client when accessing the application.
PurposeJustificationResponse: string; Justification given by the client when accessing the application.
TemporaryAccessApprovers: array[string]; List of approvers for this access request.
TemporaryAccessDuration: int; Approved duration for this access request.
UserUID: string; The uid of the user who logged in.
